9年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=34adbcac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=4ca497db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=536a3334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=50af163a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b548fcb4ec7f5f21f1faae414cb129476d6e3ac","tid":1743741,"uid":83582,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T10:50:09.000Z","msg":"荃灣文宣組 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113105994adc33a0aba2d2ab43b91a916757c917","tid":1743741,"uid":338743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20