<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ng18607704/status/1196632031314137094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNg18607704%2Fstatus%2F1196632031314137094&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=36689c57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNg18607704%2Fstatus%2F1196632031314137094&h=20f75937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Ng18607704/status/1196632031314137094</a>"},{"pid":"a36b3ea93e0ba850c0962e2dcf00d38a19766152","tid":1743741,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df4fa796fabf728dd4ec952321a9b570a8a4c3d","tid":1743741,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"全香港最撚紅既地區"},{"pid":"c23f462530b5ec8da9b28de41be30650b97c4d94","tid":1743741,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c089ee20ae5fb8b10a34554947edc93e6e76fe","tid":1743741,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e0480af33e3d30ce85c9665185b63b30d597d9","tid":1743741,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:10:56.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推喔"},{"pid":"a96f2b116749a07bd1f0a72a0ad434974489dada","tid":1743741,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:11:06.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳吸引火力黎推post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor 想體力升級/心態提升為民請命手足參考<br />\n補師我要幫全世界身心升level<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入黎補補正能量整理下個人狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人夠正能量先頂到落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各做所長<br />\n若要勝利 必須備戰<br />\n營養＋運動 身心感覺同樣重要<br />\n<br />\n極權將破 在支爆前會係最黑暗嘅時候<br />\n幾艱難 損失都要打落去<br />\n<br />\n和理勇武強身強心飲食入門：<br />\n全世界維持健康打落去<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要有自衞隊身體質素<br />\n香港人 團結反抗 無退路<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 8.心理健康 正能量撚❤️<br />\n當我地遇到情況📍 在安全情況下<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎做自己鍾意的事<br />\n😀約定 定期運動放鬆 <br />\n🧠睇書/聽Motivation Video<br />\n🔥最緊要痴住正能量嘅朋友/人<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\nHerbalife  健康教練<br />\n唔係重點 重點係大家要長命幫手贏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民皆兵</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢 好多五毛<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地要內在夠強 百毒不侵<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 長期抗爭致勝<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需TG 唔問名 <br />\n幫你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動打仗飲食法<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n得閒係屋企做下運動放鬆<br />\n行一陣街吸哂TG 暈低仲點打落去<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=f5cadc8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=237fae83\" d